==Exhibitions== He held an exhibition in [[Brussels]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.muzeumkarykatury.pl/wystawy/bruksela_2011/bruksela_kuczynski_en.html|title=Paweł Kuczynski - Satirical Drawings}}</ref>
In 2015 he exhibited at Cartoon Xira soon after the [[Charlie Hebdo]] incident.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://culture.pl/en/event/the-controversial-kuczynski-at-cartoon-xira|title=The Controversial Kuczyński at Cartoon Xira}}</ref>
